<div><head>《阮子政論》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.2">漁人張網于淵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.3">以制吞舟之魚；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.4">明主張法于天下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.5">以制強梁之人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.6">立法以隄民百姓不能干，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.7">立防以隄水江河不能犯。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.8">防而可犯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.9">則江河成災；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.10">法而可干，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.11">則百姓成害。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-1a.12">馬總《意林》卷四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.2">不樹者死無棺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.3">不蠶者身無帛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.4">不績者凶無縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.5">《意林》卷四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.6">君子暇豫則思義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.7">小人暇豫則思邪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-2a.8">《意林》卷四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.2">高鳥相木而集，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.3">智士擇土而翔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.4">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.5">一盜不誅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.6">害在穿窬；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.7">修譽不誅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.8">害在詞主。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-3a.9">《意林》卷四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.2">交遊之黨為，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.3">馳騖之所廢。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.4">《文選》卷五十五〈劉孝標絕交論〉注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.5">裁國無利器，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.6">猶鉛而而望其巧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.7">《北堂書鈔》卷二十七、《太平御覽》卷二百四十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.8">世多善弩而拙於弓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.9">弓無法準，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.10">故任巧由意，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.11">弩有法準故易有善。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-4a.12">《太平御覽》卷三百四十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.2">夫交遊者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.3">儔黨結於家，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.4">威權傾其國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.5">或以利厚而比，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.6">或以名高相求；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.7">同則譽廣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.8">異則毀深。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.9">朝無兩端之議，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.10">家有不協之論，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.11">至今父子不同好，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.12">兄弟異交友，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.13">破和穆之道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.14">長爭訟之源。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-5a.15">《太平御覽》卷四百六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.2">雖金玉滿堂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.3">明珠滿室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.4">飢不為寶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.5">非國之用。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1464_CHANT_001-6a.6">《太平御覽》卷八百二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
